Syntax:

if condition:
do this

else:
do this

Example Problem:

To check if given no. is even or odd

number = int(input("Which number do you want to check?"))
if number % 2 == 0:
print("This is an even number.")

else:
print("This is an odd number.")

Note:
6 / 2 = 3 -> Gives quotient
6 % 2 = 0 -> Gives remainder
